posts.title: Kendall Jenner Is The World's Highest Paid Model This Year And This Is How Much She Made
posts.content:
**So we all know that the Kardashian-Jenner clan is rich AF, but Kendall may have just pulled the most boss move of them all.**

**[Random Buzzfeed GIF]**
